{"type": "article", "id": 42914, "title": "如何和房子合影才好玩？试试这些“互动”方式｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-07-11T23:23:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 42255, "name": "Logideez"}, {"id": 42256, "name": "Rita Rivotti"}, {"id": 42257, "name": "Ugmonk"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 154, "image": "img/article/article_show/201707112140097wN3G4q0CnpsJZvV.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Architectural photography by Anna Devis &amp; Daniel Rueda</h3><p>在怎么把建筑拍得既好看又有趣这件事上，<a href=\"http://reflejodeloinvisible.blogspot.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anna Devis</a> 和 <a href=\"http://danielrueda.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Daniel Rueda</a> 这对来自西班牙瓦伦西亚的情侣有一些让人会心一笑的奇思妙想。他们通过自己的穿着打扮、所在位置以及姿势让所在的周边环境变成了可供发挥创意的画布，有些照片你可能要多看几眼才能反应过来他们是怎么拍摄的。如果你喜欢他们的摄影风格，可以关注 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/anniset/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Devis</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/drcuerda/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rueda</a> 的 Instagram。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214038lcZbNxEJegPXK2aW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112140394KSRjfvaCMQhVGJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214040GdC86iXPNrzohmwy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214038cPfGdbOt5EZhNxgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214040NsMcv7BAh1qmYjtp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214041g9mxVlDfcoy7eJz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Third Thumb by Dani Clode</h3><p>义肢设备不仅能造福残障人士，也可以为更多人的生活带来便利。当英国皇家艺术学院的毕业生 <a href=\"http://www.daniclode.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dani Clode</a> 发现义肢（prosthesis）一词的原意指的是“增加”，并非“修补”或是“替换”，她受到启发，决定开发一款能够帮到人们的可穿戴装备。这个名为 Third Thumb 的义肢相当于让人多了一根拇指，需要和安装在脚底的压力感应装置配套使用，Clode 将这个操作过程形容为像是控制缝纫机一样，习惯之后很快就能上手。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214056ZnaJ5d0OT8PRI12G.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112140572MBmEonjHgd6abeC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112140565MVE0gwc9qGaTfHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.530880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214057Hqv5ZsuCBte6dhUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.165821\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112140561aCL0KERnsxH4Noj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Logifaces by Logideez</h3><p>还记得那个可以一直拼下去的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/38442.html\">几何桌游</a>吗？由匈牙利混凝土制品品牌 <a href=\"http://www.logideez.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Logideez</a> 推出的 Logifaces 也是一款可供人们发挥想象力的几何拼图。顾名思义，Logifaces 唯一的规则只有一个，让每一块的切面能够衔接在一起即可，这也意味着它可以一直延伸下去，发展出各种不同的玩法。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/logifaces-analogue-game-for-digital-minds-logideez-02-29-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 55 美元起。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112143092Fv8ixJLDe9aNnV0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214309N4AdLYrvJZX3DfwU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214310Sp15mCOByxfHkuNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214310TRy2mD6NAYtsBeZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Gather by Ugmonk</h3><p>我们都抗拒杂乱的桌面，但一旦忙起来忘记整理之后，要找出所需的小物就会变得格外困难。为了让桌面变得清爽，美国设计公司 Ugmonk 推出了这款名为 Gather 的模块化收纳系统。它由带插槽的木制底座和具有不同功能的白色小盒组成，底座间通过两侧的磁铁吸附在一起，可以根据需要搭配出百种以上的组合。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ugmonk/gather-the-minimal-modular-organizer-that-cuts-clu\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 109 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214127NIBn5RwWvKQFu4EX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214126TpvilNHBCtEMXnYe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214126ewqanCoKEViGN8b3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214126OSApzQst6CxbJEPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Beach Glass by Beachware</h3><p>由于沙滩崎岖不平，想要喝上一杯的话，杯子的选择就变得格外重要。美国设计公司 Beachware 为此专门设计了沙滩专用的杯子系列 Beach Glass，他们在杯子下方加入了一根中间带圆球的长柄，可以稳稳地固定在沙滩上。你可以通过<a href=\"https://thebeachglass.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买这些杯子，售价为 9.99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112141507lxEPdkuiKeF61Sz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707112141508WfzuXFvYc7LaHpV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214150QlY5BXTH9p06ZO2v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tyto Alba by Rita Rivotti</h3><p>来自葡萄牙的 <a href=\"http://ritarivotti.pt/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rita Rivotti</a> 是一个专营葡萄酒品牌和包装设计的工作室，他们为酒庄 <a href=\"http://www.cl.pt/htmls/pt/home.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">Companhia das Lezírias</a> 打造的这款 Tyto Alba 是一个称得上“动物友好”的包装设计。Tyto Alba 指的是猴面鹰，由于酒庄常年致力于保护这种猫头鹰，酒名和包装都围绕它所设计。木盒上的洞眼刚好对应了标签上睁着大眼睛的猴面鹰，正面还有一根小木枝供鸟儿小憩，只要在内部加上草垫，它就能当作鸟屋使用了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214209qa3dYhfplRWDk2Pw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.197500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711214209D83xuN7UpH1EnZKh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.171250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}